@node "future" "Has it got a future?"

   Like all programs, CLI-Tracker will never be finished. So if you like
   or use this program, please let me know.
   
   If you want a feature added, tell me too.
   
   The future depends on you...
   
   If you don't send me *ANY* mail, I will just keep future versions to
   myself. :)
   
   So if you have access to Internet Email, please send me some kind of 
   feedback...
   
@endnode
